title: VA - Not To Be Sniffed At [The Great '70's B Side][2008] 3 CDs
description:
VA - Not To Be Sniffed At [The Great &#039;70&#039;s B Side][2008] 3 CD Set @ 128kbps

All the songs featured here had the dubious honour of gracing single B sides back in the day of the humble 7". Now they get THEIR chance to shine as stars of this excellent compilation!

It is recommended that this be listened to in its entirety as a programme to get the full enjoyment as great care has been taken in the deciding of running order.

The tracks featured were mainly selected from Rock Oriented singles released during the mid/late Seventies. They were NOT however taken from vinyl but from digital recordings.

Please seed for as long as possible and where possible purchase further recordings by the Artists/Bands you find interesting.
